  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Get prepared and cook your polenta </strong></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle </p>\n<p>Line a <strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">small</span> <span class=\"text-highlight\">oven-proof dish</span></strong> or tupperware (approx 15x15cm) with<strong> cling film</strong><span class=\"text-highlight\"> and set it to one side</span>.</p>\n<p>Add 400ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [800ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to a pot with the <strong>Knorr</strong> <strong>chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat.</p>\n<p>Once dissolved, gradually whisk the <strong>polenta</strong> into the <strong>boiling stock</strong>. Continue to whisk for 2-3 minutes or until a thick porridge consistency is achieved.</p>",
