    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Get prepared for the last few steps</strong></p>\n<p>Re-boil a kettle. </p>\n<p>Tear the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into small bite-sized pieces.</p>\n<p>Slice the <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half.</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>chives</strong> finely and set aside.</p>\n<p>Pat the <strong>rump steaks</strong> dry with a kitchen towel, rub them with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season both sides generously with <strong>salt</strong>.</p>",
