    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Serve up!</strong></p>\n<p>Toss the <strong>rocket</strong> and <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> with the <strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">balsamic</span> </strong><strong>dressing</strong> and serve to the side in separate bowls.</p>\n<p>Season the<strong> rested steak</strong> with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>.</p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>steak</strong> over the<strong> mushroom sauce</strong> with the <strong>polenta chips</strong> to the side.</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
